Ooh!

160
00:08:46,250 --> 00:08:46,971
Let's go!

161
00:08:46,991 --> 00:08:47,351
Yeah!

162
00:08:47,392 --> 00:08:47,992
Ah-ha!

163
00:08:48,192 --> 00:08:48,933
Yahoo!

164
00:08:49,254 --> 00:08:49,374
