00:20:21,263 --> 00:20:22,183
Do you seem to?

378
00:20:22,583 --> 00:20:26,445
What? What are you doing? Get out of my head!

379
00:20:27,005 --> 00:20:31,066
Stop struggling. Let me follow the current deep.

380
00:20:31,804 --> 00:20:33,685
deeper to its source.

381
00:20:34,225 --> 00:20:35,646
Stop! Stop!

382
00:20:36,046 --> 00:20:36,926
Aaaaah!

383
00:20:37,967 --> 00:20:42,429
Ah, with the fear is mingled guilt.

384
00:20:43,749 --> 00:20:45,830
It squirms in you like a worm.

385
00:20:47,491 --> 00:20:48,271
And the why?

386
00:20:50,412 --> 00:20:54,334
Ah, and there is its heart.

387
00:20:54,614 --> 00:20:58,056
You surprise me. I could not feel it before.

388
00:20:59,273 --> 00:21:02,235
Your feelings are a powerful shield, indeed.

389
00:21:02,275 --> 00:21:02,515
Do not...

390
00:21:03,355 --> 00:21:03,595
Whew.

391
00:21:04,295 --> 00:21:05,916
Oh man, she is so good.

392
00:21:06,236 --> 00:21:09,757
That character just holds so much weight.

393
00:21:10,177 --> 00:21:16,500
She is deliberate, careful, even, despite the very obvious power that she holds.

394
00:21:17,040 --> 00:21:21,501
And this we can tell from her voice, and it's got to influence our writing.

