00:21:36,750 --> 00:21:42,352
Yeah, I hear you. Admittedly, I'm not sure I can, although I definitely like to make an attempt,

399
00:21:42,712 --> 00:21:48,034
and yes, I am open for voiceover work. But still, I recommend that you still give it a try.

