00:22:19,253 --> 00:22:19,753
those sessions.

409
00:22:20,273 --> 00:22:24,314
But this is an opportunity to get the chance to help your characters become fully realized

410
00:22:24,754 --> 00:22:29,796
much earlier in the writing process, which I think is worth a lot more than zero dollars.

411
00:22:30,336 --> 00:22:32,456
And your product owners probably do too.

